long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Futinator is back for EA Sports FC 25!

Futinator is a powerful extension that helps to handle the EA Sports FC 25 Ultimate Team web app easier by allowing you to bind common actions (Buy now, Search, Change price, ...) to keys on your keyboard. Snipe faster than others!

Futinator can do the work for you like buying, bidding or listing.

You can change the key bindings at any time using the Futinator menu.

For best experience set Fifa Web App language to english.
